          "<em>参照: <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/satyanadella/status/2066182223213293753\">A frontier without an ecosystem is not stable</a> by Satya Nadella（原文: snscratchpad.com/posts/frontier-ecosystem/）</em>"
